            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I called them two days back asking for my son's admission in grade 3.We live in U.S.A but we are temporarily here for 2-3 months for some official work and that's why I thought about this school .The lady who picked up my call at first said that they do not provide international curriculum for this grade and then she said there is no vacancy.Still confusing !!!",
